    "description": "Fires 3 plasma projectiles that explode for elemental rocket damage. Each impact also leaves a plasma field dealing +50% elemental rocket damage over an area about 4x wider than the initial blast, and it can hit through cover. High damage, huge splash, poor accuracy. Uses 3 ammo per shot."
